<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/oil-and-pipelines-agency> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We are a statutory public corporation, sponsored by the Secretary of State for Defence, formed in 1986 by virtue of the Oil and Pipelines Act 1985. We manage, operate and maintain 6 Naval Oil Fuel Depots and a Petroleum Storage Depot on behalf of the Ministry of Defence. OPA is a public corporation of the Ministry of Defence ."@en .
